=head1 SYNOPSIS

Experimental scripts that are used to test ideas for plausibility.

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This part of the repository is a collection of experimental scripts to see how
plausible an idea. Consider them "experimental" or "exploritory".

None of the work here should be considered complete or functional at any point
unless documented otherwise. Generally, none of them are intended to be useful
beyond a proof of concept and there is no guarantee of fitness (compile or
runtime).

All work contained in this repository is copyrighted and owned by the author of
the repository at the time of publication.

